CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 1st July, 2002
10 Asadha, 1924 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from the 1st
July, 2002 : -
Shri Arun Jaitley relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of Law, Justice and Company Affairs;
i)
Shri M. Venkaiah Naidu relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of Rural Development;
ii)
i)
Dr. C.P. Thakur relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of Health & Family Welfare;
Smt. Maneka Gandhi relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of
Statistics and Programme Implementation;
iv)
Shri V. Dhananjaya Kumar relinquished the charge of the office
of Minister of State in the Ministry of Textiles; and
v)
Shri Muni Lall relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Labour.
vi)
